name: Ten of Pentacles
deep_meaning: The Ten of Pentacles combines the Earth element's focus on material, money, career, physical world with the energy of completion, fulfillment, end of cycle. This numbered card shows the progression of pentacles energy through concrete life experiences and situations.
deep_meaning_ko: 펜타클의 10는 material, money, career, physical world의 에너지를 나타냅니다.
upright_extended: The Ten of Pentacles combines the Earth element's focus on material, money, career, physical world with the energy of completion, fulfillment, end of cycle. This numbered card shows the progression of pentacles energy through concrete life experiences and situations.
reversed_extended: When reversed, Ten of Pentacles suggests challenges or blockages in material, money, career, physical world. The natural flow is interrupted.
numerology: Number 10: completion, fulfillment, end of cycle
questions_to_ask: How is the Earth energy of pentacles manifesting in my life?
What does this card teach me about material, money, career, physical world?
